1. Run npm install(mysql2, dotenv modules were added)
2. Create schema in MySQL workbench using the command 'CREATE SCHEMA hoa_db'
3. Create or use an existing .env file and place the following details:
    DB_HOST=localhost
    DB_USER=root || whatever your username is in MySQL
    DB_PASSWORD=<your password in SQL>
    DB_NAME=hoa_db
4. Run app.js